==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Railroad
<hw>Rail"road`</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To carry or send by railroad;
usually fig., to send or put through at high speed or in great haste; to
hurry or rush unduly; <as>as, to <ex>railroad</ex> a bill through
Condress</as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq., U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

